title: Duo Partner S1
body:
Whats up, 
I'm a Support Main in S1 dedicated to climbing the ladder until I reach Diamond. I'm looking for a dedicated ADC duo that is willing to learn from their mistakes and grow better at the game every game as we climb. I would consider myself a decent support at my current level and I am always looking to improve. Silver 3+ or greater is preferred so we can at least be along the same skill level. Message me in game if you are interested.

My main supports are:
Thresh 
Alistar
Tahm
Janna

replies.body: Would love to duo, but you're on NA .. this is the OCE forums lol
